        {
            "id": "13619b2b02224194",
            "type": "text",
            "x": 1400.0,
            "y": -300.0,
            "width": 250,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "## The Origins\n\nFrom Babbage's engines to Turing's logic. The dream of thinking machines.\n\n---\n\nAda Lovelace wrote the first algorithm.\nAlan Turing defined the universal machine.",
            "color": "1"
        },
        {
            "id": "b767faa37e5c4eac",
            "type": "group",
            "x": -499.99999999999994,
            "y": 800.0,
            "width": 1000,
