            "type": "text",
            "x": 200.00000000000006,
            "y": 900.0,
            "width": 250,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "## The Neural Revolution\n\nThe rise of connectionism. Perceptrons, backpropagation, and deep learning.\n\n---\n\nGeoffrey Hinton and the AI Winter.\nThe AlexNet breakthrough in 2012.",
            "color": "5"
        },
        {
            "id": "65bb7c5d787940f5",
            "type": "group",
