            "type": "text",
            "x": -1000.0,
            "y": -299.99999999999983,
            "width": 250,
            "height": 400,
            "text": "## Generative Era\n\nMachines that create. Transformers, diffusion models, and large language models.\n\n---\n\nAttention is All You Need.\nChatGPT and Stable Diffusion change the world.",
            "color": "3"
        },
